1️⃣ Go to your project folder
cd path/to/your/project

2️⃣ Initialize Git (this creates .git)
git init

3️⃣ Check file status (MOST IMPORTANT habit)
git status

4️⃣ Add files to staging area
git add .
git add filename

5️⃣ Commit (this is NOT optional)
git commit -m "Initial commit"

6️⃣ Rename branch to main (do this once)
git branch -M main

7️⃣ Add remote repository (critical step)
git remote add origin https://github.com/USERNAME/REPO_NAME.git
  Check it: git remote -v